Subject: [PATCH v10 07/18] drm: exynos: dsi: Introduce hw_type platform data
Date:   Wed, 14 Dec 2022 18:28:56 +0530
Message-Id: <20221214125907.376148-8-jagan@amarulasolutions.com>
